body:
Hi!. The recommended way to build and run SSD models in TensorFlow Lite is described [in this post](https://medium.com/tensorflow/training-and-serving-a-realtime-mobile-object-detector-in-30-minutes-with-cloud-tpus-b78971cf1193)

That uses NMS and has a postprocessing step to replace all the NMS ops with a single TensorFlow Lite Custom op.
